## Feature workflow

Domain spec → correct package → **create tests** (TDD below) → tiered runs ([issues-testing.mdc](issues-testing.mdc)) → `mvn verify` ([issues-quality.mdc](issues-quality.mdc)).

## TDD — development guidance

Default for new behaviour: write a failing test before `src/main` changes. Delegate to [`.cursor/agents/`](../agents/) or invoke by name (`tdd-red`, `tdd-green`, `tdd-refactor`).

| Phase | Subagent | Goal | Allowed | Forbidden |
|-------|----------|------|---------|-----------|
| **Red** | `tdd-red` | **Create** a failing test | New/updated test; domain-named methods | Production `src/main` changes |
| **Green** | `tdd-green` | Minimal code to pass | Smallest `src/main` diff | New tests; refactors; scope creep |
| **Refactor** | `tdd-refactor` | Improve design, tests green | Rename, extract, dedupe | Behaviour change |

**Cycle:** Red (must fail) → Green (must pass) → Refactor → `mvn test` → repeat.

Test layout: [issues-tests.mdc](issues-tests.mdc). Running tests: [issues-testing.mdc](issues-testing.mdc).
